{"runId":"openai-gpt-oss-120b-nitro@2026-05-13T22-42-40-564Z","slug":"llm-generative-ui-landscape-2026","locale":"es","model":"openai/gpt-oss-120b:nitro","modelPath":"openai-gpt-oss-120b-nitro","createdAt":"2026-05-13T22:42:49.923Z","sourcePath":"src/content/posts/2026-05-10--llm-generative-ui-landscape-2026/index.mdx","targetPath":"src/content/posts/2026-05-10--llm-generative-ui-landscape-2026/es/index.mdx","candidatePath":"reports/i18n/llm-generative-ui-landscape-2026/es/openai-gpt-oss-120b-nitro/2026-05-13T22-42-40-564Z/candidate.mdx","sourceHash":"2e0e25fcee6f590ef4844f929ffd2adc962a5ed9d43c37433a36005e483ab648","outputHash":"8dbab1d7252453ebfafa3a766e636b128a73c10c80cfac157cb34b2b368cb374","reasoningEffort":"low","temperature":0.3,"maxTokens":16000,"timeoutMs":200000,"articleSummary":"**Summary – “The LLM GenUI Landscape v2”**\n\nThe article argues that “generative UI” is an overloaded term and clarifies its meaning at runtime: the LLM decides *which UI component(s)* to display, not just what text to show. It distinguishes this from design‑time code generation, form autofill, and raw HTML injection (the latter being the most dangerous approach). The core of the piece is a three‑pattern taxonomy:\n\n1. **Tool‑to‑component rendering** – the model calls a named tool and the app maps that call to a pre‑built component (safest, used by Vercel AI SDK, CopilotKit, etc.).  \n2. **Component‑catalog composition** – the model emits a typed JSON tree referencing a developer‑defined catalog of components, which the frontend renders (mid‑risk, requires careful schema design).  \n3. **Open‑ended generation** – unrestricted markup generation (most expressive but highest security and stability risk).\n\nThe tone is an analytical tutorial, using a “map” metaphor to guide architects in choosing the appropriate layer of the stack. The intended audience is engineers and product designers building LLM‑driven interfaces, especially those evaluating trade‑offs between safety, flexibility, and implementation cost.","totalInputTokens":25889,"totalOutputTokens":9929,"totalCacheReadTokens":11520,"totalCacheWriteTokens":0,"totalDurationMs":8203,"totalCostUsd":0.002796891,"pricingSource":"local-openrouter-estimate","telemetry":{"model":"openai/gpt-oss-120b:nitro","chunkSize":"10p","totalChunks":17,"totalInputTokens":25889,"totalOutputTokens":9929,"totalCacheReadTokens":11520,"totalCacheWriteTokens":0,"totalDurationMs":8203,"totalCostUsd":0.002796891,"pricingSource":"local-openrouter-estimate","chunks":[{"index":0,"inputTokens":1287,"outputTokens":527,"cacheReadTokens":0,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":518,"costUsd":0.000145053},{"index":1,"inputTokens":1417,"outputTokens":346,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":379,"costUsd":0.000117543},{"index":2,"inputTokens":1633,"outputTokens":720,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":460,"costUsd":0.000193287},{"index":3,"inputTokens":1561,"outputTokens":460,"cacheReadTokens":0,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":480,"costUsd":0.000143679},{"index":4,"inputTokens":1487,"outputTokens":728,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":502,"costUsd":0.000189033},{"index":5,"inputTokens":1565,"outputTokens":589,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":580,"costUsd":0.000167055},{"index":6,"inputTokens":1651,"outputTokens":726,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":473,"costUsd":0.000195069},{"index":7,"inputTokens":1502,"outputTokens":579,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":419,"costUsd":0.00016279799999999997},{"index":8,"inputTokens":1561,"outputTokens":667,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":615,"costUsd":0.00018093899999999997},{"index":9,"inputTokens":1493,"outputTokens":543,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":400,"costUsd":0.000155967},{"index":10,"inputTokens":1333,"outputTokens":394,"cacheReadTokens":768,"cacheWriteTokens":0,"durationMs":411,"costUsd":0.000122907},{"inde